# Once this file exists, the Vercel CLI ignores .gitignore entirely (only
# Vercel's built-in defaults like node_modules/.git always apply), so the
# build/test/secret junk is re-listed below.
#
# Deliberately NOT listed: apps/rounding-numbers/src/assets/music/*.ogg and
# public/fonts/. The third-party tracks (FesliyanStudios, Suno, Reganati) are
# gitignored because their licences forbid redistributing the raw file in this
# public MIT repo, but they may be *used* in the app with attribution (see
# CREDITS.md). Leaving them out of this ignore list lets a CLI deploy upload
# them to the build without committing/redistributing them in Git.
#
# NOTE: Git-integration deploys (push to main) build only committed files, so
# they will NOT include these tracks — re-run `vercel deploy --prod` after a
# push if you want them in production.

# Dependencies
node_modules

# Build output
dist
build
out
*.tsbuildinfo

# Turborepo
.turbo

# Test / coverage
coverage
test-results
playwright-report
playwright/.cache

# Environment & secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Copyrighted source material (never ship)
*.pdf
lesson.pdf

# Logs / OS / editor
*.log
.DS_Store

# Harness state
.claude
